    <body lang="en-US" link="#0000ff" dir="ltr">
    {{> header unmudlLogo = unmudlLogo}}
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"><br/>
    <br/>

    </p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"> {{date}}</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in">Dear {{college.title}},</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in">This
    is to let you know that
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li/>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in">{{learner.fullname}} 
      </p>
      <li/>
    {{#if hasEmail}}
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"><b>Email:</b>
    {{learner.emailAddress}}</p>
    {{else}}
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"><b>Phone:</b>
    {{learner.phoneNumber}}</p>
    {{/if}} 
      <li/>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"><b>Unmudl ID:</b> 
      {{learner._id}}, 
      </p>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in">just
    applied for acceptance into
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li/>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"><b>Course:</b>  {{course.title}} 
      </p>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in">and their credit card has a hold for
    the course fee.  
    </p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"><b>FOR INSTRUCTORS:</b>  You don’t
    have to do anything.  This email is just an FYI that an additional
    learner has enrolled In your course.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"><b>FOR SUPERADMINS OR ENROLLMENT
    OFFICERS:</b>  Please ensure this student’s request for admission
    is taken care of as soon as possible.  If your college has not
    undergone backend integration (that is, if the request is not being
    taken care of automatically), you can accept or deny admission to
    this student  manually by logging into  
    </p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"><font color="#0000ff"><u><a href={{learnerPortalDashboard}}>{{learnerPortalDashboard}}</a></u></font>
    ,</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"><a name="_GoBack"></a>then going to
    “Learners” in the left hand menu, finding {{learner.fullname}}, clicking on
    the three dots under “Actions,”  choosing “View Profile” and
    then clicking on either the option to accept or deny their
    application to enroll in the course.  The student will receive an
    automatic notification of your decision.  
    </p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in">If the student is accepted, and you do not have backend integration you will need to follow up with a personal email/phone call with the student
    explaining when and where to show up for the course (if in person) or
    when and where to log in (if online).</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in">Thank you – and if you run into
    problems, please contact Unmudl support at
    <font color="#0000ff"><u><a href="mailto:{{supportMail}}">{{supportMail}}</a></u></font>.</p>
    
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in"><br/>
    <br/>

    </p>
    {{> footer}}
    </body>
